        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This function copies the statistics associated with the kernel object core specified by <emphasis>obj_core</emphasis> into the buffer <emphasis>stats</emphasis>. Unlike the raw statistics this may report calculated values such as averages. Note that the size of the buffer (<emphasis>stats_len</emphasis>) must match the size specified by the kernel object type&apos;s statistics descriptor.</para>
